\n<Guard><WordWrap>Op! Mayong aga po sir. What business do you have here sir?
\n<Manu><WordWrap>Mayong aga as well. Is this the Old Town Hall?
\n<Guard><WordWrap>Yes this is the Old Town Hall, why?
\n<Manu><WordWrap>Well you see I have some important business with the mayor of Gastropolis.
\n<Guard><WordWrap>The mayor? Hmmm, I cannot allow you to enter. You are not an important personnel.
\n<Manu><WordWrap>Please sir I just need to talk to him, its urgent!
\n<Guard><WordWrap>Hmmm. It seems you are really need to talk to the mayor...
\n<Guard><WordWrap>I'll let you in ONLY if you can help me in return.
\n<Guard><WordWrap>There are some chores here inside plaza libertad that has made it difficult for me to manage time. You just need to choose from the two.
\n<Guard><WordWrap>There has been a renovation of the Nelly Garden's and alot of tree's have been removed but the tree stumps. I want you to remove the tree stumps in the garden.

\n<Guard><WordWrap>Another is the church of San Jose. They have a feeding mass of the homeless people today and the people at the church are short handed in food. I want you to cook them food for the church so they can feed to the homeless.
\n<Guard><WordWrap>Lastly If its possible, I want some payment in exchange for your entrance in the Old Town Hall. I want 10,000 Gold minimum!.
\n<Guard><WordWrap>Very well. Head to the back gate of Nelly Garden and remove all the wooden stumps there. If your wondering where the Nelly Garden is its at the left side of the plaza.
\n<Guard><WordWrap>Here's an Axe to help remove all the wodden stumps from the garden.
\n<Guard><WordWrap>Return to me once you have removed all the wooden stumps from the garden.
